    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>{{ 'What do we do?' | trans }}</h2>

        <p>At Kailab we develop <em>casual games</em>, games oriented to marketing advertising and applications for mobile phones and small consoles.</p>

        <p>For this, we have been 5 years experience developing and improving two software tools that let us port any game we do to several platforms in a very short time: Fast Track Machine for JAVA, and Arcadix for C++.</p>

        <p>These tools are software libraries that programmers use when creating applications or games.</p>

        <p>Every library is composed of modules that have specific functions. For instance, the "input module" manages keyboards, mouse, touchscreens, while the "sound module" loads and manages all sounds.</p>

        <p>We are continuously improving and including new modules to our libraries. The more modules we include, the more things our applications can do, the easier to program they are.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>{{ 'Where are we?' | trans }}</h2>

        <div class="subsection">
            <div class="contact_info">
                {% include 'KailabFrontendBundle:Default:_contact.html.twig' %}
            </div>

            <div id="map_canvas" style="width: 450px; height: 250px"></div>
        </div>

        <p>Probando lalal If it changed, it's probably because some auto-indenting setting changed 
        (autoindent, smartindent, cindent, indentexpr), and/or a filetype plugin 
        was turned on or changed/updated, and/or the value of 'formatoptions' 
        changed.</p>

        <p>The standard way to avoid this is to set the 'paste' option before 
        pasting and reset it afterwards. You can make a key do this with the 
        'pastetoggle' option, too.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<script type="text/html" id="map_info">
<strong style="display: block;">{{ 'Kailab Office' | trans }}</strong>
<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?daddr=Carrer+de+Pau+Claris,+115,+08009+Barcelona,+Espa%C3%B1a&hl=es&ie=UTF8&sll=41.392053,2.167856&sspn=0.006295,0.006295&view=map&geocode=CWmQDIzzH71pFbWXdwIdMBQhAA&z=16" target="_new">
{{ 'see in google maps' | trans }}
</a>
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(document).ready(function(){
    var options = {
        zoom: 14,
        center: new google.maps.LatLng(41.391868, 2.168099),
        mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.ROADMAP
    };
    var map = new google.maps.Map($('#map_canvas').get(0), options);

    var marker = new google.maps.Marker({
        position: options.center, 
        map: map, 
        title:"Kailab"
    });


    var info = new google.maps.InfoWindow();
    info.setContent($('#map_info').html());
    info.setPosition(marker.position);
    info.open(map);

});
</script>

{% endblock %}
